r Lee\"|'''[[R. Lee Wrights]]'''\n| [[Texas]]\n!align=center|'''Vice chair of the [[Libertarian National Committee]]'''<br />(2004\u20132006)\n!align=center|<small>([[R. Lee Wrights#2012 presidential campaign|Campaign]])</small>\n|-\n|}\n\n==Presidential delegate count==\n{| border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"4\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin: 1em 1em 1em 0; background: #f9f9f9; border: 1px #aaa solid; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 95%;\"\n|- style=\"background:#e9e9e9;\"\n! colspan=\"3\" | Libertarian National Convention Presidential vote, 2012<ref name=\"ballot\">{{cite web | url=http://www.ballot-access.org/2012/05/05/gary-johnson-nominated-by-libertarian-party-on-first-ballot/ | title=Gary Johnson Nominated by Libertarian Party on First Ballot | work=[[Ballot Access News]] | date=May 5, 2012 | accessdate=May 6, 2012 | author=[[Richard Winger|Winger, Richard]]}}</ref>\n|- style=\"background:#eee; text-align:center;\"\n! style=\"width: 17em\" |Candidate\n! style=\"width: 5em\" |first ballot\n! style=\"width: 7em\" |Percentage\n|- {{party shading/Libertarian}}\n| '''[[Gary Johnson]]'''\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"| '''419'''\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"| '''70.4%'''\n|-\n| [[R. Lee Wrights]]\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"| 152\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"| 25.6%\n|- style=\"background:#eee; text-align:right;\"\n|-\n| Jim Burns\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"| 12\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"| 2.0%\n|-\n| [[Carl Person]]\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"| 3\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"| 0.5%\n|-\n| [[None of the above|NOTA]]\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"| 3\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"|  0.5%\n|- style=\"background:#eee; text-align:right;\"\n|-\n| [[Sam Sloan]] ([[Write-in candidate|Write-in]])\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"|  2\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"|  0.3%\n|-\n| [[Max Abramson]] (Write-in)\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"|  2\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"|  0.3%\n|-\n| [[Ron Paul]] (Write-in)\n| style=\"text-align:right;\"| 1\n| style=\"text-ali